These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, climbing, badminton
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | badminton | climbing | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: mango, peas, blueberry
1. the person eating peas is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating mango is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | mango | blueberry | peas |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, photography, reading
1. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | cooking | photography | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, metal, house
1. the fan of metal is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | house | metal |

