.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, writing, baking
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby   | writing | baking | video-games |

 